    <note>Wu(3) Ju [17706] He treated Chen(1) Fuliang [10585] with the li aprropriate of a disciple and did not use his affinal connection with the imperial family to be haughty. He set the policy of selecting Zhao(1) Ningzong [9013] as emperor with Zhao(1) Ruyu [3200] (an example of the imperial yindang making a decision). As a result, coalition troubles (dangshi) arose. Han(1) Tuozhou [3326] feared him. Shengzheng, p. 2322; Xianchun Linan zhi, 50.8b. CBD, 2, 1110-1.From Hartwell's ACTIVITY table:1180:  Apt. Liangzhe yunpan1182:  Promoted to LIangzhe yunfu1185:  In office as Huaidong zongling</note>
